title: Wed Post Show (10-05-22)

description:
Bobby starts by giving an update on the foxes that come up to his house regularly.

Why it’s not a good idea to eat before sleeping. We get into some crazy cheating scandals in chess and poker. We throw around the ideas of some BBS experiences we can put up for auction with charity. We get into a discussion about BeReal.
